name: Beach Bum Candid
description: I love candid photos, caught this moment that shows the lifeguard letting us slide with our kooky antics. Could have been problematic because I camouflage body painted her on set at the beach while she was naked. Not super legal. This piece is for the #picetnunc100 challenge.
